mg src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/02/030944_bd45af9647115da722f10c1fa7b89094.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F02%2F030944_bd45af9647115da722f10c1fa7b89094.jpg&h=aa14acd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n叫kacchera</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n圖load 唔到去google search <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26f46482e83fd0a243a21e41cc64e2a2d3c5c85b","tid":104033,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T19:17:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢位巴打 我點知你條內褲係點？</blockquote><br />\n唔係要圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5f25b8a1f82f30c735e8a4bb0246f5f945a7438","tid":104033,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T19:22:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你老母臭閪ust巴基閪</blockquote><br />\nBtw 錫克教教義<br />\n1. 信奉真神「真名」嚴格信仰一神論，認為神是唯一的、是全知全能的，是宇宙萬物的締造者，是公正而仁慈的。<br />\n2. 主張在神的面前人人平等，反對種姓分離與歧視婦女。<br />\n3.信仰業報輪迴說，人要靠神的惠顧和祖師的指導纔得以解脫。<br />\n4.尊崇祖師，將其奉為神的使者，並信奉祖師的預言，祖師享有無上的權力，其傳承是由前任指定自己的繼承者。<br />\n5.反對祭祀制度與偶像崇拜，主張簡化禮儀，朝拜聖地，積極入世。<br />\n唔知啱唔啱連登仔口味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"017ea911bbb756f6a836cf48ca911d65647e3f91","tid":104033,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T19:41:06.000Z","msg":"樓主我撐你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你u讀咩科?? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6292e8ec3900d91391c7508904a254dfd4ce7582","tid":104033,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T19:42:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主我撐你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你u